{"tid":1743033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有關黎明行動","createTime":"2019-11-21T04:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T06:24:14.000Z","uid":168184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77baf7729461c78bcda3ba58e307a968e73ec441","tid":1743033,"uid":168184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:41:35.000Z","msg":"大家focus錯咗？日日見黨鐵封元朗嗰邊 有咩用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n塞爆港島線佢啊！等啲人去唔到中環返工啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多人 唔洗頂門 都塞爆部車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家不斷來回搭中環至銅鑼灣，炮台山至太古呢啲站 等人過唔到海！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c017703361cbe14312ef4b7f87ce5c682a1102","tid":1743033,"uid":168184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:41:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc56b9e0240d18b3720718f1db26235967b7e85f","tid":1743033,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:42:09.000Z","msg":"中環開花有用好多"},{"pid":"3aff5bb983cc53a5c70533593794f4e3a57b6ba1","tid":1743033,"uid":168184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23a89ef357f0473697a0bce262338446f9ef0a36","tid":1743033,"uid":168184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc56b9e0240d18b3720718f1db26235967b7e85f","tid":1743033,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:42:09.000Z","msg":"中環開花有用好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"而家仲開到花？雙管齊下囉！"},{"pid":"038a815108198fd8e9be759a76285a926106a44c","tid":1743033,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=cc2e673e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=b4274c49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=abe9e8a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=a82ccda8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"9e168529ecb151926a673d3b3fa5e8c7e1fb35e3","tid":1743033,"uid":168184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed838102bd1be97484bee5b45e6b83e9dce1244c","tid":1743033,"uid":168184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:45:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e77658d133afc02349b12ead174108f94cf6b905","tid":1743033,"uid":168184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"唔想大家事倍功半"},{"pid":"5d6f009bd75b1486b105ecf73b95bf3a6244e777","tid":1743033,"uid":111448,"like